name: Bethany Black twitch.tv/beffernieblack

tweet: @connolly_lg @petefrasermusic @Scientits @alexvtunzelmann In order to give “coins” value there’s a built in limit of how many there can be, and each successive one is twice as difficult to “mine” with the Non-Fungibile Tokens they took the spreadsheet and said “now you own this jpeg” making it a very complicated digital receipt.
